{"thag1.51:0.1":"Theragatha 1.51 ","thag1.51:0.2":"Ekakanipata ","thag1.51:0.3":"Chatthavagga ","thag1.51:0.4":"Godhikattheragatha ","thag1.51:1.1":"“Vassati devo yatha sugitam, ","thag1.51:1.2":"Channa me kutika sukha nivata; ","thag1.51:1.3":"Cittam susamahitanca mayham, ","thag1.51:1.4":"Atha ce patthayasi pavassa deva”ti. ","thag1.51:1.5":"… Godhiko thero …. "}